message.text:
📣CALLING ALL ASPIRING ITHM VOCALISTS & INSTRUMENTALISTS! ⏩

Are you ready to take your talent to the next level?

 Join the ITHM MUSIC MAKERS this September 16-17 and be part of something powerful, passionate, and purpose-driven.

📍 𝘃𝗲𝗻𝘂𝗲: Alfredo Reyes Hall (ARH) 204 
📅𝗦𝗰𝗵𝗲𝗱𝘂𝗹𝗲:

SEPTEMBER 15 | MONDAY | 3:00 PM - 5:00 PM
SEPTEMBER 17 | WEDNESDAY | 9:00 AM - 11:00 AM

Pre-register through this link to choose your audition and interview schedule:
https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdedzbaeqHy8nQeF0UgLFuXLv5ODeD0m2lDRFuiCRyGPRBvlw/viewform?usp=header

For instrumentalists, submit your online auditions here: 
https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSci_vttPiZpsmBt9KbBK1A4LsUXkiLjqFgaiyF0VLXd2uWiZA/viewform?usp=header

 Bring your sound. Bring your heart. Let’s make More than Music — let’s make an impact.  ⏩

#ITHMMusicMakers #MoreThanMusicMM #AuditionCall #SeptemberSound
#GandaGalingTalinoatTalento

message.text:
[Groovers ‘25-‘26: TamHunt 2025 - Audition Guidelines]

𝗔𝗟𝗟 𝗨𝗡𝗜𝗧𝗦, 𝗥𝗘𝗣𝗢𝗥𝗧 𝗙𝗢𝗥 𝗗𝗨𝗧𝗬! 📣

The mission briefing is in: here are the guidelines for this year's TamHunt auditions. 
Gear up and get ready to deploy your skills!

🗓️ 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗗𝗮𝘁𝗲𝘀: September 15-17, 2025 (6:00 PM - 8:30 PM)
📍 𝗩𝗲𝗻𝘂𝗲𝘀: 
• Day 1 (September 15, 2025): Pavilion 2
• Day 2 & 3 (September 16-17, 2025): ARH 302-303
👤 𝗧𝗮𝗿𝗴𝗲𝘁 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝗲𝗻𝗰𝗲: Open to All FEU–ITHM Students
🔗 𝗟𝗶𝗻𝗸 𝗼𝗳 𝗥𝗲𝗴𝗶𝘀𝘁𝗿𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗙𝗼𝗿𝗺: https://bit.ly/ITHMGrooversMembershipApplications2025

📌 We also accept walk-ins! So lock and load your talents and get ready to shine!

Best of luck, performers! 🔰

Pubmat By:
Hisami Muramatsu
Ian Canlas

Caption By: Mae Saeed

#TamHunt2025 
#MembershipApplications2025
#AfterGround
#ITHMGroovers

message.text:
[Groovers ‘25-‘26: TamHunt 2025 - Audition Guidelines]

𝗔𝗟𝗟 𝗨𝗡𝗜𝗧𝗦, 𝗥𝗘𝗣𝗢𝗥𝗧 𝗙𝗢𝗥 𝗗𝗨𝗧𝗬! 📣

The mission briefing is in: here are the guidelines for this year's TamHunt auditions. 
Gear up and get ready to deploy your skills!

📍 𝗩𝗲𝗻𝘂𝗲𝘀: 
• Day 1 (September 15, 2025): Pavilion 2
• Day 2 & 3 (September 16-17, 2025): ARH 302-303

📌 We also accept walk-ins! So lock and load your talents and get ready to shine!

Best of luck, performers! 🔰

Ian Canlas

Caption By: Mae Saeed

message.text:
[Groovers ‘25-‘26: TamHunt 2025 - Audition Guidelines]

𝗔𝗟𝗟 𝗨𝗡𝗜𝗧𝗦, 𝗥𝗘𝗣𝗢𝗥𝗧 𝗙𝗢𝗥 𝗗𝗨𝗧𝗬! 📣

The mission briefing is in: here are the guidelines for this year's TamHunt auditions. 
Gear up and get ready to deploy your skills!

🗓️ 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗗𝗮𝘁𝗲𝘀: September 15-17, 2025 (6:00 PM - 8:30 PM)
📍 𝗩𝗲𝗻𝘂𝗲𝘀: 
• Day 1 (September 15, 2025): Pavilion 2
• Day 2 & 3 (September 16-17, 2025): ARH 302-303
👤 𝗧𝗮𝗿𝗴𝗲𝘁 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝗲𝗻𝗰𝗲: Open to All FEU–ITHM Students
🔗 𝗟𝗶𝗻𝗸 𝗼𝗳 𝗥𝗲𝗴𝗶𝘀𝘁𝗿𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗙𝗼𝗿𝗺: https://bit.ly/ITHMGrooversMembershipApplications2025

📌 We also accept walk-ins! So lock and load your talents and get ready to shine!

Best of luck, performers! 🔰

Pubmat By:
Hisami Muramatsu
Ian Canlas

Caption By: Mae Saeed

#TamHunt2025 
#MembershipApplications2025
#AfterGround
#ITHMGroovers

message.text:
[Groovers ‘25-‘26: TamHunt 2025 - Audition Guidelines]

𝗔𝗟𝗟 𝗨𝗡𝗜𝗧𝗦, 𝗥𝗘𝗣𝗢𝗥𝗧 𝗙𝗢𝗥 𝗗𝗨𝗧𝗬! 📣

The mission briefing is in: here are the guidelines for this year's TamHunt auditions. 
Gear up and get ready to deploy your skills!

🗓️ 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗗𝗮𝘁𝗲𝘀: September 15-17, 2025 (6:00 PM - 8:30 PM)
📍 𝗩𝗲𝗻𝘂𝗲𝘀: 
• Day 1 (September 15, 2025): Pavilion 2
• Day 2 & 3 (September 16-17, 2025): ARH 302-303
👤 𝗧𝗮𝗿𝗴𝗲𝘁 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝗲𝗻𝗰𝗲: Open to All FEU–ITHM Students
🔗 𝗟𝗶𝗻𝗸 𝗼𝗳 𝗥𝗲𝗴𝗶𝘀𝘁𝗿𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗙𝗼𝗿𝗺: https://bit.ly/ITHMGrooversMembershipApplications2025

📌 We also accept walk-ins! So lock and load your talents and get ready to shine!

Best of luck, performers! 🔰

Pubmat By:
Hisami Muramatsu
Ian Canlas

Caption By: Mae Saeed

#TamHunt2025 
#MembershipApplications2025
#AfterGround
#ITHMGroovers
